About Event

​As many of you know, I’ve been hosting this gathering for a long time—this year marks the 16th year 🤍

​The original version was always small and intimate, and that spirit remains at the heart of it.

​My home is tiny but nestled in the beautiful Redwoods, and we’ll be making joyful use of every corner.
